{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-list-template-tsx","path":"/category/sasjs-server/","result":{"data":{"site":{"meta":{"title":"Raw SAS - SAS Tips n Tricks","description":"Tips n Tricks and other SAS Titbits from around 10 years of SAS projects and tinkering about with SAS"}},"remark":{"posts":[{"post":{"html":"<h1>LOG_LOCATION in SASjs Server</h1>\n<p>Version 0.11 of <a href=\"https://server.sasjs.io\">SASjs Server</a> now has a configurable LOGS location!</p>\n<p>Logs rotate daily, and are named according to the start time - so every time you restart the server, a new log file is generated.</p>\n<p>Log content is configurable according to the <a href=\"https://server.sasjs.io/settings/#log_format_morgan\"><code class=\"language-text\">LOG_FORMAT_MORGAN</code></a> setting - here showing the source IP address, timestamp, endpoint queried, and the response code:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 750px; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.936170212765955%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"log location\"\n        title=\"log location\"\n        src=\"/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/1d69c/log_location.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/4dcb9/log_location.png 188w,\n/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/5ff7e/log_location.png 375w,\n/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/1d69c/log_location.png 750w,\n/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/78797/log_location.png 1125w,\n/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/aa440/log_location.png 1500w,\n/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/0ef7e/log_location.png 1594w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Docs: <a href=\"https://server.sasjs.io/settings/#log_location\">https://server.sasjs.io/settings/#log_location</a></p>\n<p>SASjs Server itself provides MIT open-source middleware for SAS, which can be useful as a (very) low cost option for:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Migrating legacy SAS/Intrnet or <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/easy-af-scl-modernisation-html5-sas-allan-bowe/\">AF/SCL</a></li>\n<li>SAS App Development</li>\n<li>3rd Party Integrations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you’re in the market for a vendor to deliver on the above, contact the SAS Apps team: <a href=\"https://sasapps.io\">https://sasapps.io</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Log Location","path":"/log_location/","previewImg":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":4.25531914893617,"src":"/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/ee604/log_location.png","srcSet":"/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/69585/log_location.png 200w,\n/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/497c6/log_location.png 400w,\n/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/ee604/log_location.png 800w,\n/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/f3583/log_location.png 1200w,\n/static/f8fa191f54e2486b4a4f553a13b6bc6a/374ca/log_location.png 1594w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}},"tags":["sasjs-server","sas-admin"],"date":"Jul 16, 2022"}}}]}},"pageContext":{"page":"category","archives":{"2012":8,"2013":10,"2014":4,"2015":7,"2016":17,"2017":12,"2018":9,"2019":2,"2020":3,"2021":1,"2022":7,"2023":1,"2024":1,"2025":3},"filter":{"frontmatter":{"tags":{"in":["sasjs-server"]}}},"limit":10,"skip":0,"numPages":1,"currentPage":1,"tag":"sasjs-server"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}